@joroblox92 It's not! I'm a black comic book fan girl and when the characters are messed up so badly it's hard to want to watch something that bears no resemblance to the comic books. 

The Avengers were at least more like The Ultimates. Of course liberties have to be taken for a new format but all the race and gender swapping, not to mention the sexual preference changes, well it just gets to be too much. Now we're getting a black Wonderman!?! That's just diisheartening because that's NOT Wonderman from the comics. And there are so many black super heroes they could use! 

Just because we don't like drastic changes to beloved comics doesn't make anyone racist!
